# 🛒 Hawky – Responsive Landing Page

Welcome to the official landing page source code for **Hawky**, a modern and mobile-friendly e-commerce service that brings your favorite local street cart foods directly to your doorstep.

## 📱 Overview

This project is a responsive landing page built with **HTML**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **minimal JavaScript**, designed to promote the **Hawky mobile app** and allow users to:

- Request Hawky services in their area
- View app mockup with animated food visuals
- Access Play Store & App Store links (placeholder)
- Submit contact form with basic details

---

## 🎯 Features

- ✅ Clean, modern mint green theme
- ✅ Responsive layout (mobile-first design)
- ✅ Slanted "H" Hawky logo in navbar
- ✅ App mockup section with **sliding food images** (chaya, dosa, idli, poori, pizza, noodles)
- ✅ Real Play Store and App Store icon buttons
- ✅ Contact information section
- ✅ “Request Hawky in Your Area” form with name, city, and phone number
- ✅ Smooth animations and transitions
- ✅ Built without Bootstrap or external UI libraries

---

## 🧑‍💻 Technologies Used

- **HTML5**
- **Tailwind CSS**
- **Vanilla JavaScript**

